@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - Peace Keychains</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <span class="text-6xl">☮️</span>
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-4">About Peace Keychains</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-6">
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
                In 2020, Rod and Stephani Brower started to travel more. Before retiring, Rod worked at a machine shop. 
                He put those skills to work to make peace signs to give out while travelling, with a goal of 
                <span class="font-semibold text-peace-600">spreading peace and love</span>.
            </p>

            <p class="leading-relaxed">
                They love to see where their peace signs get to, and hear any stories you might have, so please contribute!
            </p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-peace-50 to-calm-50 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-peace-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Open Source
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Peace Keychains is an Open Source, volunteer project. If you'd like to contribute, head on over to 
                    <a href="https://github.com/Pilchie/PeaceKeychains" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                       class="text-calm-600 hover:text-calm-700 font-medium underline decoration-2 decoration-calm-300 hover:decoration-calm-500 transition-colors">
                        github.com/Pilchie/PeaceKeychains
                    </a> and join in!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/submit" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-peace-500 to-peace-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full shadow-lg hover:from-peace-600 hover:to-peace-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200">
                Share Your Story
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
